# Asynchronous Group Chat

Asynchronous Group Chat is a cloud based, JavaScript powered HTML5 Web Application.
The Workspace http://datastore.asadmemon.com/faizanu94 can be changed to http://datastore.asadmemon.com/yoursecret

### Version
3.0.0

### Tech

Asynchronous Group Chat uses a number of open source projects to work properly:

* [AngularJS] - HTML enhanced for web apps!
* [Marked] - a super fast port of Markdown to JavaScript
* [Twitter Bootstrap] - great UI boilerplate for modern web apps
* [jQuery] - duh

